org.openbase.bco.ontology.lib.manager.aggregation.datatype

Class OntProviderServices

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openbase.bco.ontology.lib.manager.aggregation.datatype.OntProviderServices

  • public class OntProviderServices
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is part of a data structure to provide the BCO ontology data (state values of sensors and actuators). The custom data type OntProviderServices expresses the middle-level of the data structure (middle granularity), which includes a quantity of elements (1:N - relation). Consider in addition the data types OntUnits and OntStateChange. 1 : N 1 : N OntUnits --- (includes) --- OntProviderServices --- (includes) --- OntStateChange
    Author:
    agatting on 15.09.17.
